## Architecture Decisions

We agreed to adopt **event sourcing** for the order management system.

N> The RFC for event sourcing is available at `docs/rfc/event-sourcing.md`.

### Pros

- Better audit trail
- Temporal queries
- Event replay capability

### Cons

- Increased complexity
- Storage requirements
- Learning curve
